snippet.textDisplay: Questions like this make one rethink on the medical industry. Must we pay doctors and nurses a salary? Shouldn't we pay a gratitude fee plus standard costs? Medicine is an art. And our lives depend on the service rendered. Each person must have a say in deciding the payment.
